---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AEROS — 具身智能体的治理运行时" lang="zh">

  <!-- ═══ Section 1: Hero ═══ -->
  <section class="hero grid-bg">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-h1">AEROS</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">让具身智能体真正跑起来的运行时。</p>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        一个机器人，一个持久 Agent，一套治理运行时。<br>
        AEROS 补上了具身智能缺失的那一层：<br>
        执行管控 · 策略约束 · 故障恢复 · 行为审计。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary">预约 Demo</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/s20sc/aeros-runtime" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary">
          GitHub 源码 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-badge">运行时核心开源 &middot; Apache 2.0 &middot; 学术研究支撑</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 2: Transition Line ═══ -->
  <section class="transition-line">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="transition-text">不止于 Demo，走向可治理的部署。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 3: The Gap ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">行业缺口</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">大模型会思考了，机器人能动了，<br>但智能体还是跑不起来。</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)">
        今天的具身 AI 技术栈很强，但不完整。大模型能推理，机器人能执行。真正缺的，是让智能体在真实世界里持续跑、安全跑、受控跑的运行时层。
      </p>

      <div class="cards-grid-3">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>能推理不等于能跑</h3>
          <p>一个计划不是一个运行时。真实的 Agent 需要生命周期管理、状态连续性、任务监管、重试机制，以及环境变化时的结构化恢复。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>硬件百花齐放，软件各自为政</h3>
          <p>人形、移动操作臂、协作臂、服务机器人——每种形态不该都重建一套 Agent 栈。具身系统需要一个硬件之上的通用运行时抽象。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>上了生产就得有治理</h3>
          <p>在生产环境里，能力调用不能裸跑。需要契约校验、策略约束、实时监控、回滚路径，以及完整的审计链路。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 4: What AEROS Is ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">AEROS 是什么</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 是具身智能体的治理运行时层。</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl)">
        AEROS 处在具身智能和真实世界执行之间。它不替代模型、不替代机器人中间件、不替代硬件控制。它管的是：持久化的具身 Agent 怎么准入、怎么执行、怎么监管、怎么进化、怎么审计。
      </p>
      <p class="highlight-line">AEROS 不决定智能体想做什么。它管的是，智能体被允许怎么跑。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 5: How AEROS Works ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">运行机制</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 怎么工作</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)">
        AEROS 把具身 AI 从一次性任务执行，变成受治理的运行时流程。
      </p>

      <div class="flow-layout">
        <div class="flow-steps">
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-external">
            <span class="flow-step-num">1</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">用户目标</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-external">
            <span class="flow-step-num">2</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">Agent 规划</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-divider">
            <span class="flow-divider-label">AEROS 接管</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">3</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">能力准入</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">4</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">契约校验</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">5</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">策略检查</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">6</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">执行</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">7</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">监控巡查</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">8</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">恢复 / 回滚</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step flow-step-governed">
            <span class="flow-step-num">9</span>
            <span class="flow-step-name">审计日志</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-explain">
          <h3>每次调用都是治理事件</h3>
          <p>
            AEROS 不会盲目把规划结果丢给机器人执行。它会验证什么能跑、在什么条件下跑、用什么监控、出了问题怎么兜底。
          </p>
          <p>
            第 1-2 步发生在 AEROS 之外——任何 Agent 或规划器都可以提出动作。从第 3 步开始，AEROS 接管：检查准入、校验契约、执行策略、监督执行、记录一切。
          </p>
          <p class="flow-highlight">
            任何调用到达硬件前，都必须经过治理运行时。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 6: Three Core Layers ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">核心能力</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">三层运行时，一套完整体系</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)"></p>

      <div class="capability-grid">
        <a href="/zh/product" class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-tag">Apache 2.0</div>
          <h3>Runtime 核心</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">持久化具身 Agent 的执行底座。管理生命周期、调度、状态连续性、执行流程和运行时监管。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/product#ecm" class="capability-card">
          <div class="capability-tag">Apache 2.0</div>
          <h3>ECM 能力包</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">把具身能力封装成模块化、可安装、可进化的运行时单元。支持受控组合、跨任务和跨形态的能力复用与演进。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/product#governance" class="capability-card capability-card--commercial">
          <div class="capability-tag tag-commercial">企业版</div>
          <h3>治理层</h3>
          <p class="capability-desc">让运行时管控成为系统一等属性。在整条执行链上施加契约、权限、策略、监控、回滚和审计。</p>
          <span class="capability-link">了解更多 &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 7: Not Another Robot OS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">定位</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">不是又一个机器人 OS</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl)"></p>

      <div class="comparison-rows">
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">ROS 2</span> 解决<strong>通信</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决<strong>治理运行时</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">工作流工具</span> 解决<strong>编排</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决<strong>运行时约束下的持久执行</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-row-item">
          <div class="comparison-them">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag">模型栈</span> 解决<strong>推理</strong>问题
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-arrow-divider">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="comparison-us">
            <span class="comparison-label-tag comparison-label-aeros">AEROS</span> 解决<strong>准入、监管、恢复和策略管控</strong>问题
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="analogy-block">
        <p>Linux 给机器一个系统层。</p>
        <p>Kubernetes 给分布式应用一个控制层。</p>
        <p class="analogy-highlight">AEROS 给具身智能体一个治理运行时。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 8: What AEROS Is / Is Not ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">边界</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 是什么，不是什么</h2>

      <div class="is-isnot-grid">
        <div class="is-column">
          <h3 class="is-isnot-heading is-heading">AEROS 是</h3>
          <ul class="is-list">
            <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> 持久化具身 Agent 的治理运行时</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> 能力执行与演进的基础层</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> 监管、恢复与策略执行系统</li>
            <li><span class="check-icon">&#x2713;</span> 具身 AI 部署的审计与管控面</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="isnot-column">
          <h3 class="is-isnot-heading isnot-heading">AEROS 不是</h3>
          <ul class="isnot-list">
            <li><span class="x-icon">&#x2717;</span> 不是又一个机器人中间件</li>
            <li><span class="x-icon">&#x2717;</span> 不是硬件驱动框架</li>
            <li><span class="x-icon">&#x2717;</span> 不只是模型推理栈</li>
            <li><span class="x-icon">&#x2717;</span> 不是 Demo 编排玩具</li>
            <li><span class="x-icon">&#x2717;</span> 不是 ROS 插件</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 9: Five-Layer Architecture ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">架构</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">五层运行时架构</h2>

      <div class="arch-layout">
        <div class="arch-stack">
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 5: Agent</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">应用逻辑 &amp; 决策</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer arch-governance">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 4: Governance</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">策略执行 &amp; 审计</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 3: ECM Package</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">能力模块 &amp; 契约</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 2: Runtime</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">生命周期 · 调度 · 执行</span>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-arrow">&darr;</div>
          <div class="arch-layer">
            <span class="arch-name">Layer 1: Embodiment</span>
            <span class="arch-desc">硬件抽象 &amp; 传感器</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arch-text">
          <h3>治理，<br><em>从第一行代码开始</em></h3>
          <p>
            传统机器人中间件把治理当补丁——部署完了再加监控。
            AEROS 不一样。治理是运行时的一等原语，每次能力调用到达硬件前，都得先过治理引擎。
          </p>
          <p>
            结果：安全是架构保证的，不是靠祈祷。
            能力升级是受控的，不是听天由命。
            审计链路是完整的，不是抽样的。
          </p>
          <a href="/zh/technology" class="btn btn-secondary">
            深入架构设计 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="arch-summary">这五层把智能和执行纪律分开，把执行纪律和硬件依赖分开。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 10: Use Cases ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">落地场景</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">为真实具身部署场景而生</h2>

      <div class="usecase-grid">
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <div class="usecase-icon">&#x1F916;</div>
          <h3>人形机器人</h3>
          <p>跑持久化具身 Agent，能力执行受治理管控，生命周期可管、能力进化可控。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <div class="usecase-icon">&#x1F9BE;</div>
          <h3>移动操作</h3>
          <p>在统一运行时下协调导航、感知和操作，带监控和恢复。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <div class="usecase-icon">&#x1F3ED;</div>
          <h3>工业与企业</h3>
          <p>给生产机器人 Agent 工作流加上策略约束、灰度发布和审计能力。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <div class="usecase-icon">&#x1F504;</div>
          <h3>跨形态迁移</h3>
          <p>运行时逻辑跨机器人形态复用，不用每换一种机器人就重建整套 Agent 栈。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 11: What Exists Today ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">已有成果</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">已经做到哪了</h2>

      <ul class="proof-list">
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 开源运行时核心——已上线</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> ECM 能力包工作流——已定义并文档化</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 治理管线，含 Watcher 监管机制——MVP 已实现</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 架构与评估协议——7 篇论文公开可查</li>
        <li><span class="proof-check">&#x2713;</span> 早期演示——在典型具身任务上跑通了治理执行</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="proof-closing">AEROS 不只是概念。它正在成为一个可部署的运行时底座。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 12: Research ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">学术根基</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">有研究支撑，靠系统驱动</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl)">
        AEROS 的背后是一整套关于具身运行时系统、治理、能力契约和部署基准的研究计划。目标不是发几篇散装论文，而是给具身智能定义一个新的系统层。
      </p>
      <div class="research-ctas">
        <a href="https://s20sc.github.io/aeros-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">查看研究计划</a>
        <a href="/zh/technology" class="btn btn-secondary">
          深入架构设计 <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 13: CTA by Audience ═══ -->
  <section class="section grid-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">开始</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">开始探索</h2>

      <div class="audience-grid">
        <div class="audience-card">
          <h3>开发者</h3>
          <p>看文档、跑运行时核心、研究架构设计。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="/zh/open-source" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">查看文档</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/s20sc/aeros-runtime" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">GitHub 源码 &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card audience-card--highlight">
          <h3>合作伙伴</h3>
          <p>看 AEROS 怎么在真实系统中实现具身 Agent 的治理部署。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">预约 Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-card">
          <h3>研究者</h3>
          <p>跟踪运行时、治理和具身系统基础设施的研究路线图。</p>
          <div class="audience-ctas">
            <a href="https://s20sc.github.io/aeros-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">查看研究</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Section 14: Brand Line ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-line">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="brand-text">具身智能体的治理运行时。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ═══ Hero ═══ */
  .hero {
    padding: 140px 0 120px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-base);
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(0,102,255,0.10) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 20% 80%, rgba(0,194,168,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 80% 60%, rgba(0,102,255,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    top: -100px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,102,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(60px);
    animation: hero-pulse 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @keyframes hero-pulse {
    0% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.15); }
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  .hero-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .arrow { margin-left: 4px; }

  /* ═══ Transition Line ═══ */
  .transition-line {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
